(1, 'VUI KHỎE CÙNG TÂM ĐỨC', '1681797175_vui-khoe-td-thu-2.jpg', '<p><strong>VUI KHỎE C&Ugrave;NG T&Acirc;M ĐỨC</strong></p>\r\n<p>Số ph&aacute;t s&oacute;ng thứ 2 của chương tr&igrave;nh &ldquo;<strong>Vui khoẻ c&ugrave;ng T&acirc;m Đức</strong>&rdquo; với chủ đề &ldquo;<strong>Tăng huyết &aacute;p kh&aacute;ng trị</strong>&rdquo; sẽ l&ecirc;n s&oacute;ng v&agrave;o l&uacute;c&nbsp;<strong>15h00 thứ 6 ng&agrave;y 15/05/2020</strong>. Chương tr&igrave;nh được t&agrave;i trợ bởi&nbsp;<strong>c&ocirc;ng ty Medtronic</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14930\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/icon10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"8\" height=\"12\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Đến với chương tr&igrave;nh lần n&agrave;y,&nbsp;<strong>BS. Đinh Đức Huy, Gi&aacute;m đốc Nội Tim Mạch Bệnh Viện Tim T&acirc;m Đức</strong>, sẽ c&oacute; những ph&uacute;t gi&acirc;y tr&ograve; chuyện hữu &iacute;ch, hấp dẫn c&ugrave;ng với qu&yacute; kh&aacute;n giả.</p>\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14930\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/icon10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"8\" height=\"12\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng đ&oacute;n xem chương tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; tham gia<strong>&nbsp;minigame</strong>&nbsp;để nhận được những phần qu&agrave; c&oacute; gi&aacute; trị nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n<p><img class=\" wp-image-16485 aligncenter\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/vui-khoe-td-thu-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"299\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Để tham gia, quý khán giả vui lòng thực hiện đầy đủ các bước sau:</p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14928\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/h2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Bước 1</strong>: Like fanpage&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/benhvientimtamduc/\">@benhvientimtamduc</a>&nbsp;, tham gia event.</p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14928\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/h2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Bước 2</strong>: Trả lời câu hỏi trong hình bên dưới bằng cách comment đáp án bạn chọn (A, B, C, D) cùng 1 số bất kỳ từ 100-999 và tag 3 người bạn (ví dụ: A 123 @Lee, @Giang, @Ann).</p>\r\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14928\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/h2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp; Bước 3</strong>: Like và share bài viết này về tường ở chế độ công khai (public).</p>\r\n<p>Dựa vào số bất kỳ quay được từ trang www.random.orf, người nào có câu trả lời chính xác, nhanh nhất cùng con số trùng hoặc gần đúng với số random sẽ nhận được phần quà của chương trình. Trong trường hợp có nhiều người trùng số, người nào có comment sớm hơn sẽ được nhận thưởng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Giải thưởng:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&ndash; 1 Giải đặc biệt: Một khán giả có câu trả lời chính xác và con số trùng hoặc gần trùng và trả lời sớm nhất sẽ dành được phần quà đặc biệt là 1 máy đo huyết áp.</p>\r\n<p>&ndash;&nbsp;5 giải khuyến: 5 người có câu trả lời chính xác, con số gần đúng và muộn hơn sẽ nhận được phần quà là 1 card điện thoại trị giá 100.000đ.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14931\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/iconcheck4.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"15\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Kết quả của trò chơi sẽ được công bố vào cuối buổi livestream.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cùng tham gia minigame và đón xem chương trình nhé !!</strong></p>', '2023-04-18'),
(2, 'CÙNG TÂM ĐỨC NÂNG NIU NHỮNG TRÁI TIM TRẺ THƠ', '1681797376_nang-niu-tt-tre-tho-425x370.jpg', '<div id=\"seasidetms_row_vmrn36p36\" class=\"seasidetms_row seasidetms_color_scheme_default seasidetms_row_top_default seasidetms_row_bot_default seasidetms_row_boxed\">\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_row_outer_parent\">\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_row_outer\">\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_row_inner\">\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_row_margin seasidetms_11\">\r\n<div id=\"seasidetms_column_o3uamflez7\" class=\"seasidetms_column one_first\">\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_column_inner\">\r\n<div id=\"seasidetms_heading_2sykx9yw7g\" class=\"seasidetms_heading_wrap seasidetms_heading_align_center\">\r\n<h1 class=\"seasidetms_heading\">C&Ugrave;NG T&Acirc;M ĐỨC N&Acirc;NG NIU NHỮNG TR&Aacute;I TIM TRẺ THƠ</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"seasidetms_text\">\r\n<p>Hưởng ứng &ldquo;<strong>Tháng hành động vì trẻ em trong ngành y tế TP Hồ Chí Minh năm 2020</strong>&rdquo; với chủ đề &ldquo;<strong>Chung tay bảo vệ trẻ em, phòng chống xâm hại trẻ em</strong>&rdquo; của&nbsp;<strong>Sở Y tế &ndash; Ủy ban nhân dân TP Hồ Chí Minh</strong>.&nbsp;<strong>Bệnh viện Tim Tâm Đức</strong>&nbsp;tổ chức &ldquo;<strong>Chương trình khám tim mạch và tư vấn sức khỏe miễn phí cho trẻ em từ 0 đến 16 tuổi trên địa bàn thành phố</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14931\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/iconcheck4.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"15\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Đến với<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">&nbsp;chương trình này, các bé sẽ được tham gia:</span></p>\r\n<p>+ Khám Tim mạch chuyên sâu (đ&atilde; chốt đủ số lượng).<br>+ Góc trò chơi có thưởng &ldquo;<strong>Trái tim vui nhộn</strong>&rdquo; v&agrave; thi vẽ tranh &ldquo;<strong>Những tr&aacute;i tim sắc m&agrave;u</strong>&rdquo;.<br>+ Góc tư vấn cho phụ huynh và các bé &ldquo;<strong>Giữ gìn một trái tim khoẻ</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14930\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/icon10.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"8\" height=\"12\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Chương tr&igrave;nh d&agrave;nh cho tất cả c&aacute;c em từ 0-16 tuổi tham gia.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15230\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/iconcheck.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Thời gian: 13h00-16h00 ng&agrave;y 27/6/2020</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-15230\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/iconcheck.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"12\" height=\"10\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Địa điểm: Bệnh viện Tim Tâm Đức &ndash; 04 Nguyễn Lương Bằng &ndash; Phường Tân Phú &ndash; Quận 7.</p>\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, c&aacute;c b&eacute; c&oacute; thể vẽ tranh tại nh&agrave; v&agrave; gửi cho fanpage để được đăng tải tr&ecirc;n fanpage v&agrave; website. Sẽ c&oacute; 1 phần thưởng khuyến kh&iacute;ch trị gi&aacute; 200,000 đồng d&agrave;nh cho bức tranh gửi qua trang nhận được nhiều b&igrave;nh luận, lượt like v&agrave; chia sẻ nhiều nhất.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14928\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/h2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;Chương tr&igrave;nh mong muốn mang đến cho c&aacute;c em nhiều điều th&uacute; vị v&agrave; bổ &iacute;ch.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-14928\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/h2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"21\" height=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\">&nbsp;<strong>Hãy cùng Bệnh viện Tim Tâm Đức &ldquo;NÂNG NIU NHỮNG TRÁI TIM TRẺ THƠ&rdquo;&nbsp;<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-16609\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/icon-tim.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"19\" height=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\"></strong>!</p>\r\n<p>C&ugrave;ng xem lại một số h&igrave;nh ảnh của chương tr&igrave;nh:</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-16664 aligncenter\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" srcset=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho.jpg 425w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho-133x300.jpg 133w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho-350x791.jpg 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"425\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-16665 aligncenter\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho1.jpg 600w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho1-188x300.jpg 188w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho1-580x928.jpg 580w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho1-350x560.jpg 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-16666 aligncenter\" src=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho2.jpg 600w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho2-188x300.jpg 188w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho2-580x928.jpg 580w, https://tamduchearthospital.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/nang-niu-tt-tre-tho2-350x560.jpg 350w\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\r\n<p><img class=\"siz